Adding recurring entries to ledger.

<!-- more -->

@hyperlink["https://www.ledger-cli.org/"]{Ledger} lacks a way to create recurring entries for things that happen regularly and consistently, like rent payments.
Having to manually enter these kinds of entries is tedious and error-prone at best, so I wrote a quick utility to make doing this easy.

